@minbaev the main change is here fd9049c83d9ef181170d18467b16f35fc5f11599  and [here](https://github.com/rclone/rclone/blob/master/backend/s3/v2sign.go) is the v2signer.

I'd recommend you try to make a new provider for IBM and you can make it install its own auth using the same techniques as in the signer.

The new sdk is quite flexible - you can change stuff everywhere and you'll see lots of examples in the new code.
